Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.57,0:15:13.99,SoraOto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ta là vô đối!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.83,0:15:23.16,SoraOto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thế nào, Master?
